game.name: Jungle TD
game.description:
You have played different types of tower defense games so far. The fact is that you never get bored with it and start seeking a new game following the same strategy. But, a game with some useful modifications can appeal you amazingly. Do you remember that how many 3D towers you have protected yet? Your answer is none or maybe a few numbers!  Today we have brought to you a brand new adventure challenge with a needful upgrade to our huge category of classic Tower Defense games â€“ Jungle TD. 
You will see millions of dangerous monsters marching on your way in this one of the best war games for kids. Your job is to clear these horrible hordes and make people around your city tension free in this 3D tower defense game. Be careful and try to react fast before they attack on you! Do your best to defend your fortress deep within this horrible jungle! The best part is that you will also have a range of weapons including powerful plasma cannons and missiles to fight against these monsters. 
Keep your eyes open as your enemies can come from any of the directions! Place the right defenses at the right spots to complete your missions fast! Choose the right weapon and make a right strategy to finish all in this one of the best monster games for kids! Use your mouse to move on your map and try to build up to at least 5 different types of towers! There are three unique levels to play, numerous towers with a different ability and a fun-filled environment to enjoy, no download required.
